      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. FROST CAT is an improving colt who landed his fourth course and distance victory (in five overall starts) on return from a short break attempting latest. Hard to dismiss on all evidence. 3. VITE VITE was a close second beaten a neck here in a handicap last time. This a better line-up but is good enough to play a major role. 4. KHIOS is promising and still providing first campaign. Scored past two outings latterly a 6L win here trying 1900m. Rates a strong contender for securing another victory. 6. CREATIVE MIND is a three-time winner. Second at Bursa (1200m) last start. Well beaten only outing at Izmir though that was a G2. In the mix.\",\"runners\":[2,3,4,6],\"exclusive\":false}",
